TextEng: Yes, please give me Helm's blessing.
No thanks, but have you any other services?
No thanks. Carry on with your work.
Could you answer some questions for me?
Have you any other services?
Thank you, that will be all.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Tell me about Desther, your superior.
What does your holy symbol mean?
What do you know of the Wailing Death?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병에 대해 뭘 알고 있죠?

TextEng: Blessing? Yuh, that be good.
No blessing. Me want stuff. You sell any?
Text: 축복 필요 없어. 나 물건 원해. 파는 거 있어?

TextEng: No, no. Me go now.
Me got questions.
Me want stuff. You sell any?
Text: 나 물건 원해. 파는 거 있어?

TextEng: Okay. Me go now.
Me still want stuff. You sell any?
Text: 나 아직도 물건 원해. 파는 거 있어?

TextEng: What services do you offer?
What dat necklace all you priesties wear?
Text: 너희 신관들 다들 걸고 다니는 그 목걸이는 뭐지?

TextEng: Dat Wailing, dat plague stuff - what you know 'bout it?
Text: 그 울부짖는 죽음 역병-그거 뭐 알아?

TextEng: What do you know about the prison riots?
Text: 감옥의 폭동에 대해 뭘 알고 있죠?

TextEng: What you know 'bout prison riots?
Me gots other questions.
I have some other questions.
That mean you gots gold on yous?
Text: 그럼 너 금 가지고 있다는 거야?

TextEng: So you have gold on you, then?
Eh, no reason. Me ask other questions now, okay?
Text: 아, 이유 없어. 나 다른 질문 할게, 알았지?

TextEng: No reason. Let's go back to some other questions.
You gives it, now! Me maybe kill you for it!
Text: 금 내놔! 나 그것 때문에 죽일지도 몰라!

TextEng: Hand it over! I'll kill you for it!
Me sorry. Me not really gonna hurt yous.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 진짜로 다치게 하려는 거 아니었어.

TextEng: Forgive me, I did not mean to actually harm you.
Me serve Aribeth. Nobody balme me if you found dead!
Text: 나 아리베스 섬겨. 너 죽어 있어도 아무도 나 탓 안 해!

TextEng: I serve Aribeth. Nobody will blame me if you are found dead!
Text: 난 아리베스를 섬겨요. 당신이 죽어 있어도 아무도 날 탓하지 않을 거예요!

TextEng: Show what you gots, then.
Show me what you have, then.
